          p
            | I want to know, have you ever seen the rain?
          form.margin-base-vertical
            p.input-group
              span.input-group-addon
                span.icon-envelope
              input.form-control.input-large(type='text', name='email', placeholder='jonsnow@knowsnothi.ng')
